OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FStorm Darragh brought damage and
OL,7,Fdisruption across Wales after heavy
OL,8,Frain and wind caused fallen trees,
OL,9,Fflooding and power cuts.
OL,11,FThe storm hit on Saturday, 7 December,
OL,12,Fwith thousands of homes left without
OL,13,Fpower and major travel disruption as
OL,14,Fpeople were told to stay indoors.
OL,16,FA yellow warning for wind was in place
OL,17,Funtil 6pm on Sunday, 8 December.
OL,19,FOne of the areas worst affected by
OL,20,Fheavy rainfall is Builth Wells.
