OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FResidents posted videos on social
OL,7,Fmedia on Saturday evening showing the
OL,8,Fextend of some of the flooding.
OL,10,FGwyn Davies, owner of The Fountain
OL,11,FInn, posted a video on Facebook
OL,12,Fshowing water levels rising both
OL,13,Finside and outside the pub with the
OL,14,Fcaption: "4 inches deep inside and
OL,15,Fholding."
OL,17,FBuilth Wells Town Council posted a
OL,18,Fstatement on social media saying:
OL,19,F"Thankfully the water has started to
OL,20,Frecede and now the clean up begins.
