OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,F"Big thanks to the team from Penmaenau
OL,7,Ffarm who have cleared The Strand
OL,8,F(A483) and reopened the road.
OL,10,F"Unfortunately the public toilets near
OL,11,Fthe river on The Groe (as can be seen
OL,12,Fin the photo) will have to remain
OL,13,Fclosed until we can get them properly
OL,14,Fcleaned."
OL,16,FThe National Grid said there were
OL,17,Falmost 58,000 properties without power
OL,18,Fin mid and south Wales.
