OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FScottish Power Manweb said more than
OL,7,F114,000 of its customers had been
OL,8,Faffected by Storm Darragh.
OL,10,FBy 2.30pm on Sunday, over 655 separate
OL,11,Fincidents on the power network had
OL,12,Fbeen reported.
