OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FSP Manweb had arranged for a catering
OL,7,Fcompany in Anglesey to provide hot
OL,8,Fmeals to those without power, while it
OL,9,Fwas also working with the Red Cross
