OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FLiam O'Sullivan, SP Manweb director,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The prolonged duration of the
OL,8,Fhigh winds and unsafe conditions
OL,9,Fhampered our engineers' repair works
OL,10,Fin some areas, but we are making good
OL,11,Fprogress now that the wind speeds are
OL,12,Fsubsiding with more homes being
OL,13,Freconnected at pace.
