OL,3,CCommunities flooded and thousands left
OL,4,Cwithout power after Storm Darragh
OL,6,FThere were road closures across Wales,
OL,7,Fincluding the M48 Severn Bridge in
OL,8,FMonmouthshire, due to high winds.
OL,10,FTransport for Wales asked passengers
OL,11,Fto check timetables before travelling
OL,12,Fas many trains were cancelled.
OL,14,FGreat Western Railway said the severe
OL,15,Fweather had left all lines blocked
OL,16,Fbetween Cardiff Central and
OL,17,FCarmarthen, with services "unlikely"
OL,18,Fto resume before 12pm on Sunday.
